            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            印度大阅兵，这五个细节还有看头          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">牛弹琴</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                牛弹琴              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">牛弹琴</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">bullpiano</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">最睿智地解读国际风云、财经要闻，传播正能量</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><section style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;" data-mpa-powered-by="yiban.io"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035065" data-ratio="0.5625920471281296" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVePOJyMgrYs3IJZIdfJyrGWa7sp5MEKSOic54ibXlekqF1HQ9VFpaIVlxA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="679" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);"></section><section class="channels_iframe_wrp wxw_wechannel_card_not_horizontal"><mp-common-videosnap class="js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_iframe videosnap_video_iframe" data-pluginname="mpvideosnap" data-url="https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7YmwgiahniaXswqzg0yqUhKocQxjHicRjVmTPDm8MHG8rtuY4l0PjugN1ScZDvg9sbuLpibcDLmAXmX5O0pQHSM97H7icNOPJUSwtwwEA&amp;bizid=1023&amp;dotrans=0&amp;hy=SH&amp;idx=1&amp;m=&amp;scene=0&amp;token=AxricY7RBHdX24OvicIVicUJEoARnOiafpF6lLoqibicicr7rdib0n3QniaFVgwfehehHic0GtJlkFBAq2psE" data-headimgurl="http://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/XtVrzGFx5vUC6Ofq3UUamelr3NARSib1ylX3icU58lgrE/0" data-username="v2_060000231003b20faec8c5e28a1dc5d2cd05e837b0773aa28795a5f37bac7f2632d919cd3394@finder" data-nickname="牛弹琴" data-desc="男女都会！印度共和国日阅兵，女兵表演摩托车上“叠罗汉”" data-nonceid="10015965952588959386" data-type="video" data-mediatype="undefined" data-authiconurl="" data-from="new" data-width="608" data-height="1080" data-id="export/UzFfAgtgekIEAQAAAAAADgEirItHlAAAAAstQy6ubaLX4KHWvLEZgBPEx6FQfCR4ErSFzNPgMIvBnswDN-FTH93Z71ugjny3" data-isdisabled="0" data-errortips=""></mp-common-videosnap></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">空气中的雾霾很重，但挡不住印度的阅兵热情。</span></strong></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">1月26日，印度共和国日，印度举行了盛大的阅兵式和游行。戴着红头巾的莫迪格外高兴，法国总统马克龙也来共襄盛举。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">环顾整个世界，印度可能是最爱阅兵的国家了，从共和国日到独立日，从甘地生日到各个军种生日，都要阅兵，让人看得眼花缭乱。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">今年还是印度第75个共和国日，阅兵式格外盛大。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035064" data-ratio="0.5825892857142857" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVeZhbfnr5prGbMkvibIzUNsQ8YMuZDf7JnBsJ1J2x3PD9HIzf9LicrjslQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="896"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035063" data-ratio="0.6733780760626398" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVezkJNaZickxPYibCXJdBt3CdsBSQ8EDm7LkjckPTkXMfgbia7wVe2rxtgg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="894"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035062" data-ratio="0.7092592592592593" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVeAL5ic6FruzFb4Zon11SOOblK2rMB1uwWkVBVmBrx0fwdgU1r28bUBQA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035061" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVeo5icajVuCOHP85SxnLR6YQdQ0FEqUCXeKqbr8PB9lgd2qia5Nvl3ahpQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">五个很有看头的小细节吧。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">细节一，印度亮出了自己最得意的家底。</span></strong></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">主战坦克、导弹、火箭炮，以及战斗机等各种武器，都依次亮相。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">但这都是常规动作，今年印度最得意的，我感觉，<span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;">还是印度的航天。</span></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">去年，印度的“月球三号”，成功将探测器送入月球，印度也成为继美国、苏联及中国之后，第四个实现月球软着陆的国家。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">这样盛大的成就，怎么可能不展示一下呢？</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">而且，要不止一次地展示。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035067" data-ratio="0.7185185185185186" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVemxARQZaMTgnc73kuoJUgJ0C9YoQySrC5wZ2mmRew9MWppEB01A3OFA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035068" data-ratio="1.499074074074074" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVetZvhQJVCMeygMke4RHaIoVfolcSE0UC0FNILibSEMOa7icOzP1vm7Opg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">细节二，世界上最五颜六色的军队。</span></strong></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">华丽的服饰，五颜六色，甚至五花八门。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">但他们真的是军队。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">我不是军事专家，但有一个感觉，<strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">如果要评世界上最五彩缤纷最华丽夺目的军队，印度军队如果说自己是第二，那没有一支军队敢说第一。</span></strong></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">让人眼前一亮的，还有印度的骆驼部队，骆驼装饰得比姑娘还漂亮。一路走去，绝对拉风。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">只是不知这样的部队，战斗力如何？</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035066" data-ratio="0.612037037037037" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVeD54toKxcaYnbic8dbLqIAdT6DibB4XIUPicoAiaGGhZnLSNkC9dcXPkHKw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035070" data-ratio="0.6797752808988764" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVeGfPIiaqtATDxIW2fkM6XFSosZBcyjmImbBklbe5GuuOtd64SdHVzbEQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="890"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035069" data-ratio="0.6741071428571429" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVek5t85bXJ9z7DrTiaR5LUSyDYM9w3d5Ptr3Rg8icYZwuvllpdlnia8SUdA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="896"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035074" data-ratio="0.6681465038845728" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVeL35T81HMogWlp32jc0EVyRFo0eafbAQbRicTyhZbFC3hp063v2afdCw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="901"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035072" data-ratio="0.6692913385826772" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVedaQKNSaX84y9tjSjRBwgFHrBu1SEOaGibHIAzYAsllwvDJv6tgsMwQg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="889"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">细节三，印度女兵真漂亮。</span></strong><br></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">这就不需要多说了。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">印度女性权益有待提升，但印度姑娘确实漂亮，更别提还五光十色。<span style="font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></span></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035075" data-ratio="0.67152466367713" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVe7y2jGCB6ssmugoicZ0hkh4eUaVrGcq2WKacz6Hy1DwAae2IE3LZVCTw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="892" style="text-align: center;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035073" data-ratio="0.6696428571428571" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVeaH3Z1SeGHfJk4PX5P315aic4CQs7PXOyuiaFzcpVUR5UsicAeSvfl9ibBg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="896"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035071" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVedMspKGyhehr6GLX9mjSHYjY5KP0e1MOVNjILdL7lreGwmhwxXyh2Zg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">细节四，最神奇的压轴表演。</span></strong></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">我们中国人应该也很熟悉的印度叠罗汉。<br></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">别笑，我们的军队，估计就做不到。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">想一想，在高速行进当中，几个人，甚至几十个人叠在一起，难度还是挺大的。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">这次阅兵，我看了一下，有的一辆摩托车上，就有八九个印度士兵，还各种持枪射击动作。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">环顾世界，也只有印度军队，能有这么高超的叠罗汉本事了。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">莫迪也很为此自豪，我看到，他转的有限几张照片中，有一张就是40多人的叠罗汉，绝对的牌面。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035079" data-ratio="0.6689113355780022" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVe7KenSyX3wVmjC9bRXqy0bdT9WCY4f0kibgSbu1ORhegBGjica8FrqMBA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="891"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035078" data-ratio="0.6674082313681868" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVek1doP526koDSOuAfianuHd6hr6iaMDFjgA0lQhjIty4J4nYBBzlibACTQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="899"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035080" data-ratio="0.6640625" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVe071SbcZwVy0Ta3nntA4oAaj47RBIicX6m8MTGPF3dbpKjMzd3aGia53A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="896"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">细节五，一面很大很大的防弹玻璃墙。</span></strong></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">这一次，莫迪特意请来了马克龙。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">可能看惯了拉胯的法国阅兵，看到印度这别开生面的一幕幕，马克龙也是啧啧称奇，连连点赞。<br></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">但那么多人，发生意外怎么办？<br></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">别忘了，当年的埃及萨达特，就死于阅兵现场的刺杀。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">各国有各国的高招，有的加强安检，对人员进行严格审核；有的，比如像印度，干脆直接装了一面硕大的防弹玻璃墙。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">你们好好表演，我们隔着防弹玻璃看。<br></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">不对不说，这也很印度。</section><section style="text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035085" data-ratio="1.7962962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/sUFR89w6YZoNAVNiaibqibSYldqwZqKbT3BuKYvBVywQtzcb6jlbl0ibL3wSMe81LkW1ic8ibzL7T0SgmiaUAH7asfDKg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035077" data-ratio="0.7546296296296297" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVej1QbPDoXaGK1XcQhCHVpWhjd0uNdyMLXJL1Go0c5yqWUaQz6bUeaPQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035076" data-ratio="0.6962962962962963" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVe9icaegHGicFxKh4hwYJzVDPiakPibSHfQolNFg2ukkwclNT2Pu2MybPnfA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">最后，怎么看？</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">还是三点粗浅看法吧。<br style="outline: 0px;"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">第一，印度很复杂。</span></strong></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">绝对比我们中国更复杂。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">很简单，你看到哪国阅兵，有这么丰富多彩的服饰，有这么五颜六色的军队，有这么多各路大仙登场。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">至于有人评价，“阅兵式展现了印军的强大实力”。嗯，这就见仁见智了。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035082" data-ratio="0.6636871508379888" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZoNAVNiaibqibSYldqwZqKbT3BhwoW8cn7r9VP7wCO287hHSiafJo52icdZoAdvysoKg51Gv1RwhQDia8nA/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="895"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">第二，莫迪很得意。</span></strong></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">莫迪肯定还是很得意的。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">前几天，他亲自出席罗摩神庙落成仪式。这座神庙的地址，是矗立了几百年的古老清真寺。扒了清真寺盖印度教神庙，莫迪就是做成了。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">现在，又是盛大阅兵式。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">拜登虽然不给面子，答应来了，临时又放鸽子；但马克龙赶过来救场，来共襄盛举。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="504035081" data-ratio="0.6753100338218715" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/sUFR89w6YZpj3MFn7d2YVCFYnammVDVeyfHicdOWzBTOBrcYwHmZYNTOA5enPquI7YORnZ3IZLQPNJQxbysVDKQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="887"></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">第三，我们真别小觑了印度。</span></strong></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">这个观点，我已经重复多遍了。<br></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">完全是我个人的看法，<strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">如果盘点未来的世界大国，从资源禀赋和发展潜力看，我总认为，最可能的，只有这三个：美国、中国和印度。</span></strong></section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">最近几年的印度，尤其让人另眼相看。发展是硬道理，千万别折腾。我们不能因为喜欢或不喜欢印度，就漠视印度的发展和潜力，包括印度的软实力。</section><section style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;line-height: 1.75em;">谢谢印度精彩阅兵给我们带来的视觉享受和欢乐。但<strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);">因为在后面紧追的印度，因为印度的巨大发展潜力，还因为印度的对中国的各种猜忌，我们除了加快发展向上提升，别无退路！</span></strong></section><section style="text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(171, 25, 66);"></span></strong></section><section class="channels_iframe_wrp"><mp-common-videosnap class="js_uneditable custom_select_card channels_iframe videosnap_video_iframe" data-pluginname="mpvideosnap" data-url="https://findermp.video.qq.com/251/20304/stodownload?encfilekey=rjD5jyTuFrIpZ2ibE8T7YmwgiahniaXswqzHsiaA5x8JYJtR9zibdHHIjAX1dIIoxNevbyNTbQDdp3yLXKgoyBymWbD9dicBG4va5gHHMDeBurSKHcgtC535ibgag&amp;bizid=1023&amp;dotrans=0&amp;hy=SH&amp;idx=1&amp;m=&amp;scene=0&amp;token=cztXnd9GyrF01SBF5CgWicUT7iapGdZibVVkcfBibf1mOjToLafoMUaFg6Pd2jdkxnPLfp5FWAHoy8U" data-headimgurl="http://wx.qlogo.cn/finderhead/XtVrzGFx5vUC6Ofq3UUamelr3NARSib1ylX3icU58lgrE/0" data-username="v2_060000231003b20faec8c5e28a1dc5d2cd05e837b0773aa28795a5f37bac7f2632d9